{
  "stem": "5103.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In that five days there was-- I remember this, because it-- it-- if anything I remember, it was quite horrendous.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every so often if there was a break and they thought they could do it, they'd put some water down or something to drink.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had like parcels of something to nibble, dry stuff.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Dry-- I remember dry something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all we did was under there, was-- my mother, who was having menstruation, she was the only female-- mature female there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She had to do all her indignities in front of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was nothing she could do about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I saw it all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She had to do whatever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And everybody went to the toilet on the chamber pot and had to dig it in the sand.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was a stench of something unbelievable in there-- under there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was an indignity, I tell you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was something, that-- and I was just like-- like a mute.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because every time we heard the boots walking on top, there was somebody checking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Somebody had given some kind of an inkling that they were hiding somebody there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But every third or fourth day, they would come and knock and open-- open the door.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And open-- right through the house, the boots marching through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And of course, these people said no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There's nobody here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were under the-- we were really frightened stiff.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Eventually, that was cleared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Five days later, they left the area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They had moments like that where they used to indiscriminately keep on, keep on, keep on, till they actually thought maybe they'll find something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But they didn't and we came out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But the-- the family Visser said, we can't keep you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This is too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
